Program: The Forum
Title: Steel
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p030mb9q
Last Broadcast Date: Wed 2 Sep 2015
Steel has been produced for thousands of years, but is it time to find a greener alternative to the metal alloy which built the global economy ? Exploring the unique properties of steel, its strength and versatility, are materials scientist Mark Rainforth, historian of steel-pan music Kim Johnson and the South African artist Marco Cianfanelli. Photo; a steel band performing at a music festival (BBC) Show less